Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-----------------------------------------------------------Dialogue
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.00,0:00:05.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拉撒 議會違反了真主的教義
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.34,0:00:10.86,Notes,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,{\fs20\an2}阿撒迪斯坦王國 寺院
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.52,0:00:08.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本國的土地是真主所賜予的聖地
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.50,0:00:11.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟企圖將異教徒引入這契約之地
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.80,0:00:15.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,改革派終有一天會奪走我們這塊土地
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.76,0:00:19.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拉撒 只要您一句話 民眾就會揭竿而起
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.68,0:00:20.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在正是時候
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.81,0:00:22.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請鎮靜
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.68,0:00:27.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,違背教義的皇女和議會 總有一天會受到神罰
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.87,0:00:30.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們只要等待真主的報應即可
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.35,0:00:35.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這話您要說到什麼時候
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.83,0:00:39.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣下去的話 我們也會步庫爾吉斯的後塵
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.31,0:00:43.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們將成為真主之矛 對改革派施以神罰
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.42,0:00:45.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,將異教徒趕出這片土地
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.97,0:00:48.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓倒行逆施的改革派嘗嘗神怒
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.87,0:00:51.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一切榮光都將屬於我們
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.25,0:00:53.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對忘卻教義者施以神罰
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.77,0:00:55.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拉撒 拉撒…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.97,0:01:01.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了 槍聲
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.90,0:01:03.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道說是改革派的那些傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.02,0:01:05.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拉撒 亂黨們…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.48,0:01:12.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來者何人
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.84,0:01:15.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們把這裏當成什麼地方了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.70,0:01:20.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,中東
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.29,0:01:26.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,位於這裏的眾多國度 本由石油輸出產業支持經濟
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.17,0:01:32.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但由於太陽能發電系統的建設計劃 其存在價值正逐漸喪失
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.74,0:01:35.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在聯合國的決議下
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.37,0:01:39.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,除少數外 大部分石油輸出都受到了限制
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.43,0:01:43.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,部分反對的中東國家行使了武力
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.57,0:01:44.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戰火逐漸擴大
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.43,0:01:49.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是持續了二十年之久的太陽能發電紛爭
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.17,0:01:56.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在這場紛爭中經濟疲軟 又被世界排斥的眾多中東國家
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.50,0:02:00.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由於貧困不斷地分裂與合併
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.86,0:02:04.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是中東的現狀
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.12,0:02:13.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,位於裏海與波斯灣之間的阿撒迪斯坦王國 也是面臨此種困境的中東國家之一
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.54,0:02:19.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,六年前合併了內政惡化的鄰國 庫爾吉斯共和國
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.92,0:02:22.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作為新興國家復興了王制
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.44,0:02:32.41,Notes,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,{\fs20\an2}阿撒迪斯坦王國 王宮
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.41,0:02:29.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由於對國教的不同解釋 國民被分成了兩大派系
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.27,0:02:32.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,政局持續動盪
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.56,0:02:39.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說瑪斯德•拉夫瑪蒂被人劫持了？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.07,0:02:41.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然會發生這種事
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.37,0:02:46.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,保守派估計會認定是我們改革派干的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.00,0:02:50.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 這也可能是事實
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.72,0:02:54.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聯合國的支援看來只能給我們帶來災難呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.56,0:02:57.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太陽能發電計劃可是得到議會通過了的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.16,0:03:01.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但並不是所有國民都接受了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.80,0:03:05.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,議會已經決定出動治安部隊了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.75,0:03:11.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,保守派激進人士出現過激行為也只是時間問題了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.81,0:03:16.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,並且 萬一瑪斯德•拉夫瑪蒂已經死亡的話
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.66,0:03:18.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別說了 不吉利
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.93,0:03:23.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請考慮一下吧 為了避免最糟糕的事態
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.85,0:03:28.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最糟糕的…事態
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.53,0:03:32.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…內戰
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.53,0:03:41.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,忘卻教義的人 接受神怒吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.31,0:03:50.12,Notes,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,{\fs20\an2}UNION轄區 領空內
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.62,0:03:50.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無法聯絡普特萊瑪奧斯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.36,0:03:53.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從L4點回來還需要花一些時間
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.36,0:03:59.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果阿撒迪斯坦發生內戰的話 只好用當前的戰力來應對了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.58,0:04:04.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.89,0:04:06.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你那邊的情況如何
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.71,0:04:10.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各處發生著小規模紛爭 沒什麼大事
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.55,0:04:12.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請立即前往國外避難
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.78,0:04:14.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我留在這裏
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.34,0:04:16.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,留下來？ 為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.55,0:04:19.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想見證這個國家的走向
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.51,0:04:24.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且 你們將如何行動 也想親眼確認
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.41,0:04:31.05,Notes,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,{\fs20\an2}經濟特區 東京 JNN本社
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.48,0:04:30.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從200年前起查了查
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.57,0:04:36.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,獲得博士稱號的人中失蹤的和下落不明者 共有138名
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.99,0:04:39.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最近的失蹤者能查出來嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.73,0:04:40.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.54,0:04:41.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,特報
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.71,0:04:46.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿撒迪斯坦的宗教領袖 瑪斯德•拉夫瑪蒂被武裝勢力劫持了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.80,0:04:48.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿撒迪斯坦？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.70,0:04:51.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了採訪聯合國的技術支援 應該有特派員過去了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.75,0:04:53.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快聯絡 讓他報告情況
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.47,0:04:53.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.52,0:04:57.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會來嗎 「天人」
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.30,0:04:58.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大概吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.67,0:05:04.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 好美味的樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.63,0:05:07.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也不必特地送禮物來嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.18,0:05:12.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說了吧 媽媽就怕物質攻勢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.58,0:05:13.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過是一張批薩嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.17,0:05:15.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說你
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.18,0:05:15.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.75,0:05:17.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這身打扮是？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.55,0:05:20.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我正在這家店打工
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.16,0:05:23.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽 沙慈的父母很早就過世了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.91,0:05:26.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在和姐姐兩人相依為命
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.72,0:05:29.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 他的雙親都…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.17,0:05:32.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以才特地去打工
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.56,0:05:35.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真董事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.37,0:05:36.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪裏 也沒那麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.85,0:05:38.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽淚腺脆弱
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.47,0:05:39.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可這也太脆弱了吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.11,0:05:42.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是叫沙慈君 對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.25,0:05:43.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 是的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.74,0:05:46.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仔細瞧瞧長得還挺英俊的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.86,0:05:48.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎 是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.13,0:05:50.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真像呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.35,0:05:52.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃 像…什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.17,0:05:54.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有點我丈夫當年的影子呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.01,0:05:55.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪有啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.76,0:05:57.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸他還活著呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.27,0:06:05.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拉撒
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.73,0:06:07.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,馬斯德•拉夫瑪蒂
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.81,0:06:09.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.18,0:06:12.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,終於下定決心了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.43,0:06:12.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.32,0:06:16.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我決定即位成為本國的皇女
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.46,0:06:20.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪怕只是新生阿撒迪斯坦的象徵
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.66,0:06:22.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是個花瓶
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.98,0:06:24.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要我力所能及
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.14,0:06:27.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定在所不惜
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.33,0:06:28.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以 拉撒
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.07,0:06:33.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼 我就持反對的立場吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.45,0:06:35.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為… 為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.88,0:06:39.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽好 瑪莉娜公主
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.59,0:06:42.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使國家能夠重生
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.38,0:06:45.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居住在這片土地上的人民也有歷史
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.32,0:06:46.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有家人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.73,0:06:48.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有真主的教誨
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.79,0:06:50.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會有很多人厭惡變化
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.00,0:06:53.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也是其中之一
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.92,0:06:58.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了避免反對你們的人引起紛爭
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.98,0:07:02.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也需要有人接受他們的思想
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.75,0:07:06.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拉撒
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.02,0:07:08.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我所做的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.64,0:07:10.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是錯誤的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.75,0:07:13.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,席琳
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.03,0:07:17.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,議會能接受我的意見嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.47,0:07:18.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓雙方協調…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.26,0:07:20.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在不是這種情況
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.42,0:07:22.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,保守派杯葛了議會
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.71,0:07:29.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而改革派正欲接受UNION暗地裏承諾的軍事支援
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.49,0:07:32.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣做的話 只會刺激到保守派激進人士
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.97,0:07:35.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且 UNION為什麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.44,0:07:38.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使保護這個國家 也無利可圖
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.38,0:07:39.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.68,0:07:40.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.68,0:07:41.78,Notes,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太平洋上空
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.09,0:07:45.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,中尉 看來能遇上久違的Gundam了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.30,0:07:46.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遇不上久麻煩了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.91,0:07:49.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過 竟然向阿撒迪斯坦出兵
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.83,0:07:53.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是軍部上層向議會施壓的結果
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.32,0:07:56.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可不能落後人革聯哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.68,0:08:01.38,Notes,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,{\fs20\an2}阿撒迪斯坦王國 沙漠地帶
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.56,0:08:02.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,內戰開始之前
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.09,0:08:05.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兩位請在機內等候
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.60,0:08:08.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然地方不大 但已準備好了房間
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.43,0:08:10.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是周到啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.76,0:08:12.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,賓館~ 賓館~
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.22,0:08:13.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.55,0:08:16.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了平息阿撒迪斯坦的內亂
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.04,0:08:19.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,必須保護被劫持的瑪斯德•拉夫瑪蒂氏
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.14,0:08:23.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,向全國表明其平安
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.15,0:08:23.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話雖如此
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.12,0:08:26.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但這個國家的人排斥異文化
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.99,0:08:28.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知能有多少成果
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.94,0:08:30.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也出動吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.53,0:08:31.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.52,0:08:33.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是阿撒迪斯坦出身
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.77,0:08:34.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.73,0:08:36.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個國家的？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.01,0:08:37.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剎那
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.37,0:08:38.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別因故國危機
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.26,0:08:41.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就感情用事哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.42,0:08:42.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.51,0:08:47.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,劫持瑪斯德•拉夫瑪蒂氏的組織
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.13,0:08:50.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有很大機率不是改革派
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.52,0:08:52.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是Veda的推測
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.26,0:08:54.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,保守派自導自演的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.23,0:08:56.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也有可能是第三方勢力
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.97,0:09:00.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有人想在這個國家
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.18,0:09:02.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,引起紛爭
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.47,0:09:10.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那種事
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.81,0:09:13.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還想繼續嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.77,0:09:28.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小哥 要買水嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.94,0:09:30.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 我還夠
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.01,0:09:33.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是第一次來這裏吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.13,0:09:35.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一直在世界各地旅行
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.05,0:09:40.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吶吶 我聽族長說了 世界上有很高的塔
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.92,0:09:42.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還能上宇宙 這是真的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.30,0:09:45.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 是真的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.88,0:09:47.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道說你去過
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.61,0:09:48.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.72,0:09:51.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好帥 瑪莉娜殿下說了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.66,0:09:53.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總有一天我們也能上宇宙
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.07,0:09:54.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瑪莉娜
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.05,0:09:56.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不認識？ 看
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.95,0:10:00.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那些海報上的就是瑪莉娜•伊斯邁爾殿下
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.99,0:10:07.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瑪莉娜•伊斯邁爾
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.59,0:10:09.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 你在幹什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.54,0:10:11.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是庫爾吉斯人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.62,0:10:12.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看長相就知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.96,0:10:13.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爺爺?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.32,0:10:16.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裏不是你該來的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.73,0:10:18.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快滾出去
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.48,0:10:28.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒想到 居然會向UNION要求支援
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.32,0:10:33.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們應該不知道軍方也有保守派的人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.95,0:10:44.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要想辦法逃出這裏
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.63,0:10:49.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣下去這個國家又會再次陷入動亂時代
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.35,0:10:57.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼 這次真主會選哪邊呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.09,0:11:01.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過 無論選哪邊都得打仗吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.26,0:11:10.99,Notes,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,{\fs20\an2}太陽能發電接收天線設施
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.41,0:11:15.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.87,0:11:23.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在此地橫行的異教徒們 接受神罰吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.44,0:11:26.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,地點D內交戰
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.91,0:11:28.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然目標是接收天線嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.98,0:11:30.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們上 Flag Fighter
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.79,0:11:31.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.28,0:11:38.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,中尉 是自相殘殺
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.78,0:11:39.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.00,0:11:41.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪邊是叛軍
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.08,0:11:43.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雷達竟然…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.06,0:11:49.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.59,0:11:52.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這粒子光束的光芒
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.79,0:11:53.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是Gundam嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.75,0:11:57.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全彈命中 全彈命中
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.42,0:11:59.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還好在這裏待機
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.48,0:12:00.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過還不夠靈活
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.04,0:12:04.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼 是導彈
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.50,0:12:09.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,數量太多了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.43,0:12:22.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太陽能接收天線被破壞了？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.21,0:12:24.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底是誰
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.92,0:12:27.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,負責警衛的MS機師中
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.04,0:12:31.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,似乎混入了保守派激進人士
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.21,0:12:32.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼會
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.35,0:12:37.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,簡直就像預測到瑪斯德•拉夫瑪蒂會被劫持
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.19,0:12:43.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道是有周密計劃的行動 不會吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.03,0:12:51.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈瓦德 達利爾 追擊發動導彈攻擊的敵機
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.63,0:12:53.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Gundam交給我
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.47,0:12:54.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.04,0:12:55.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Gundam就拜託你了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.34,0:13:04.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂 UNION不是負責防衛阿撒迪斯坦嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.91,0:13:06.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然目的是我們
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.79,0:13:09.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打你個正著
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.91,0:13:18.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人稱格拉漢姆特別版
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.47,0:13:20.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈羅
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.97,0:13:22.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白 明白
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.18,0:13:25.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有第二次了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.90,0:13:29.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 我射偏了？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.34,0:13:30.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這機師是誰
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.62,0:13:33.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再讓我說一句吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.14,0:13:36.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,格拉漢姆•艾卡是也
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.59,0:13:40.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,踹上來了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.73,0:13:48.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然逼我使用防禦短劍
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.71,0:13:51.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,防守很嚴密嘛 Gundam
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.27,0:13:53.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.22,0:13:54.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.61,0:13:59.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接住了？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.92,0:14:03.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟敢對我的Flag…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.26,0:14:05.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這傢伙有點不尋常
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.08,0:14:10.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈羅 中止散步GN粒子 所有動力轉向火炮系統
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.12,0:14:11.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白 明白
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.98,0:14:13.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,區區一台Flag
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.05,0:14:14.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Gundam
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.39,0:14:19.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿撒迪斯坦澤伊爾基地內有MS開始行動
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.16,0:14:20.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,目標似乎是王宮
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.91,0:14:22.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,緊急通信？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.86,0:14:22.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請緊急前往壓制
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.74,0:14:27.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恐怕其他基地也會有所行動
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.27,0:14:28.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿撒迪斯坦軍？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.95,0:14:33.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,澤伊爾基地的MS擅自出動？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.81,0:14:35.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道是政變
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.00,0:14:38.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,MS一共有5台
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.33,0:14:39.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,直奔這裏而來
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.01,0:14:41.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,公主殿下 請去防空洞避難
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.86,0:14:42.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.48,0:14:43.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請趕快
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.69,0:14:45.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們是真主之矛
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.16,0:14:47.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們將揭竿而起
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.64,0:14:52.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,向忘記真主教義的人 施以神怒
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.53,0:14:56.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,消滅褻瀆契約之地的異教徒
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.43,0:15:03.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用避難嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.59,0:15:06.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,利馮茲 你也可以看看
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.18,0:15:09.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Gundam這種存在
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.60,0:15:14.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剎那•F•清英
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.62,0:15:16.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Exia 驅逐目標
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.95,0:15:23.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,貌似政變了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.77,0:15:26.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您可怎麼辦呢 Flag的機師同志
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.83,0:15:30.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難得邂逅Gundam
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.84,0:15:34.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然遺憾 但我也是吃軍糧的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.42,0:15:40.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈瓦德 達利爾 前往首都防衛
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.16,0:15:40.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.09,0:15:42.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,發射導彈的人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.09,0:15:46.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然看到過類似MS的機影 但因為特殊粒子的原因…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.60,0:15:49.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Gundam的能力也是把雙刃劍呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.38,0:16:12.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就是Gundam
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.71,0:16:14.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,靠蠻力
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.52,0:16:16.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太過依賴Gundam的性能了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.84,0:16:21.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,機師是剎那•F•清英來著？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.16,0:16:24.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.21,0:16:28.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卡茲納基地也有MS出動
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.25,0:16:30.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正經過第七區
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.29,0:16:30.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.20,0:16:33.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 接二連三的沒完沒了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.04,0:16:44.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裏是？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.43,0:17:41.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Exia
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.00,0:18:30.28,Notes,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,{\fs20\an2}阿撒迪斯坦內亂「天人」介入
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.00,0:18:26.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在接受聯合國技術援助的中東阿撒迪斯坦王國
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.00,0:18:30.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「天人」進行了武力介入
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.47,0:18:35.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿撒迪斯坦王國因為對宗教的不同理解而引起內亂
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.95,0:18:33.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿撒迪斯坦是哪來著
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.49,0:18:35.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 應該是中東的…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.33,0:18:36.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別那麼親熱啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.87,0:18:37.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在其接受聯合國援助
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.38,0:18:40.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正打算開始接收能源供應時
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.34,0:18:41.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們為何…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.30,0:18:47.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,皇小姐 Veda發來緊急暗號通信
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.27,0:18:50.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿撒迪斯坦發生武裝政變
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.90,0:18:55.68,Notes,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,{\fs20\an2}阿撒迪斯坦王國 首都
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.14,0:18:59.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,增援部隊控制了整個首都圈的制空權
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.85,0:19:05.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,信仰過剩就會引來這種悲劇嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.23,0:19:10.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡 真有你的 Gundam
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.72,0:19:13.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好戲還沒開始呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.01,0:19:19.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爆發政變
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.26,0:19:25.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還讓「天人」介入
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.25,0:19:27.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在UNION軍隊正在進行保護
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.08,0:19:30.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,政變也趨於平息
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.38,0:19:31.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請放心
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.86,0:19:37.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是 在國民心中卻點起了憤怒的火焰
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.25,0:19:42.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我把這個國家引向了戰爭
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.66,0:19:47.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請保持威嚴 瑪莉娜•伊斯邁爾
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.69,0:19:50.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還沒有結束 還沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.67,0:20:00.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真慘啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.53,0:20:03.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,發現Exia 發現Exia
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.17,0:20:09.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剎那
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.29,0:20:24.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.05,0:20:26.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成不了Gundam
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.03,0:20:33.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,萬念俱灰的剎那面前出現了阿利•阿爾•薩謝斯
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.47,0:20:35.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了根絕紛爭
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.09,0:20:37.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Exia再次站起
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.49,0:20:40.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下回 聖者歸來
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.07,0:20:42.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剎那 化作Gundam

